content: Our trading model's now at 58.3% accuracy. But here's the real question: how do we make sure our trading platform isn't just guessing, but actually promoting ethical trading? It's a marathon, not a sprint, to align our tech with our values.

Just got some wild feedback from a neuroscientist on our trading model. Turns out, our biases are messing with our trades. We're now at 58.5% accuracy, but the real challenge? Making AI outsmart our own flawed judgments.
